{"tid":993891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警破倫敦金騙案拘14男女 涉款逾6億元","createTime":"2019-01-24T09:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T16:42:03.000Z","uid":19289,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0172c8e6f25b2ec2fc8b43901a0077bc7a184d4f","tid":993891,"uid":19289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T09:16:32.000Z","msg":"警方破獲歷來最大宗倫敦金騙案。警方東九龍總區重案組成功搗破一個有組織的大型倫敦金行騙集團及拘捕14人，涉及騙款總額達6.29億，案中至少有7名受害人，其中損失最慘重的一名長者被騙去超過1億元。警方稱相信尚有其他受害人，故損失總金額料將進一步增加。<br />\n<br />\n警方於去年10月尾接獲一名男子報案，指懷疑墮倫敦金騙局，東九龍總區重案組接手跟進，經深入調查後，鎖定一個以投資倫敦金為名的詐騙集團，並涉及另外至少6宗同類案件。<br />\n<br />\n東九龍總區重案組總督察譚威信表示，該犯罪集團招聘年青人做經紀，以cold call及社交媒體隨機接觸受害人，自稱有豐富投資經驗，又對受害人噓寒問暖博取信任，相約見面後再游說他們投資倫敦金，並誘騙簽署授權文件，讓經紀全權操作戶口。受害人將款項直接存入公司戶口或個人戶口，但其後獲悉投資失利，全數輸清。<br />\n<br />\n譚威信指，據調查所得，在2016年6月至2018年10月之間，至少7名受害人墮騙局，他們分別來自香港、台灣、澳洲、加拿大及新西蘭，損失總值約6.29億元，當中最大單一損失金額超過1億元，受害人為一名年逾八旬港翁，騙徒多次聲稱蝕錢，不斷要求增加投資金額，結果一年間就血本無歸。<br />\n<br />\n警方於去年11月至今年1月之間進行首輪「冰極」行動，拘捕6男1女，年齡介乎32至62歲，直至本周二(22日)再進行第二輪拘捕行動，突擊搜查香港多個地點，包括該集團位於東九龍的辦公室，拘捕6男1女，年齡介乎20至72歲。警方於兩輪的拘捕行動中共拘捕12男2女，被捕人士來自香港、內地及新加坡，涉嫌串謀詐騙，當中包括集團主腦、前任及現任董事、經紀及戶口持有人。警方透過反詐騙協調中心(ADCC) 凍結一個銀行戶口內的2.2億元，並撿獲大批電話、電腦、提款卡、手錶及少量現金。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190124/59179376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190124%2F59179376&d=tV9qdyV9zZdslbmYcqdCeIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4f5cdd3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190124%2F59179376&h=84d7d01d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190124/59179376</a>"},{"pid":"f470b7f93b66c79b64118f7d00086188fa2cde16","tid":993891,"uid":33693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T09:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034dea50d6505e8e80f8656cc18dfe87f7016e91","tid":993891,"uid":99960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T09:25:33.000Z","msg":"邊間?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad60593993c8624d4878224c6ec0cb21b2120115","tid":993891,"uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"有一億比人呃咁勁<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得d老千咁富貴"},{"pid":"a80036866c510ab007e5dc11a6fed6bfae9a0f5e","tid":993891,"uid":219128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T09:36:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lkKiU23vbXk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlkKiU23vbXk&d=tV9qdyV9zZdslbmYcqdCeIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f6ae47f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lkKiU23vbXk</a>"},{"pid":"9973b1ee6811838d99c25ceb240a35c92cdd9085","tid":993891,"uid":229675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"今次邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b74f2fe25c0851c9435f98a3ec4bcad25c5b81f","tid":993891,"uid":50050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5bfc59d0897dc0181a75ef646ef7a120ebfa80","tid":993891,"uid":199074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"差佬係咁掃 d金融雞以後點生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebef3ac55d0c1016d05d45420a47f6d7f5bb4f8","tid":993891,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T10:03:31.000Z","msg":"我都想有一億俾人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif